In the year 2025 we paused to celebrate a day that holds immense value, Teacher Appreciation Day.

2
00:00:06,426 --> 00:00:12,580
Since time immemorial, educators have been the silent heroes, shaping our world one mind at a time.

3
00:00:13,180 --> 00:00:19,254
They ignite curiosity, inspire creativity, and instill knowledge in their students.

4
00:00:19,234 --> 00:00:21,137
But why is this day so significant?

5
00:00:21,777 --> 00:00:24,681
Firstly, it's a reminder to express gratitude.

6
00:00:25,300 --> 00:00:31,007
Teachers work tirelessly, often beyond the school bell, ensuring our children receive quality education.

7
00:00:31,608 --> 00:00:35,993
Yet they seldom receive recognition for their dedication and commitment.

8
00:00:36,593 --> 00:00:41,798
Teacher Appreciation Day serves as an opportunity to thank them for their unwavering efforts.

9
00:00:42,619 --> 00:00:45,883
