10
00:00:45,862 --> 00:00:50,750
The wisdom and skills learned in a classroom translate into opportunities and success in life.

11
00:00:51,490 --> 00:00:58,640
Good teachers empower students to dream big, equipping them with the tools necessary to make those dreams a reality.

12
00:00:59,301 --> 00:01:01,765
Lastly, it encourages community involvement.

13
00:01:02,366 --> 00:01:06,893
Parents, students and local businesses are all encouraged to show their appreciation on this day.

14
00:01:07,573 --> 00:01:14,284
Small gestures like notes of gratitude or providing classroom supplies can make a world of difference for our educators.

15
00:01:14,263 --> 00:01:19,269
So, let's join hands in 2025 to celebrate Teacher Appreciation Day.

16
00:01:19,870 --> 00:01:24,075
Let's thank our teachers, honor education, and foster community spirit.

17
00:01:24,697 --> 00:01:30,603
Remember, education is not the filling of a pail, but the lighting of a fire.

18
00:01:31,305 --> 00:01:35,170
So, light up your teacher's day on Teacher Appreciation Day 2025.

